            <p class="hero-kicker">Thought Leadership & Transformation</p>
            <h1>Ideas about business transformation, A.I., and meaningful change.</h1>
            <p>The Transformation Thread explores how organizations make better technology decisions, adopt A.I. thoughtfully, and connect strategy, systems, and people into meaningful change.</p>
            <div class="brand-page-actions">
              <a class="hero-cta" href="mailto:info@etalsolutions.tech?subject=The%20Transformation%20Thread%20Inquiry">Ask About Transformation Work</a>
