          <div class="brand-detail-grid">
            <article class="brand-detail-card">
              <strong>Who it helps</strong>
              <p>Leaders, operators, builders, and curious readers who want practical thinking about transformation without empty buzzwords.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="brand-detail-card">
              <strong>What it offers</strong>
              <ul><li>Articles and perspective pieces</li><li>A.I. and transformation themes</li><li>Practical frameworks for decision-making</li></ul>
